    Spanish (es) , Plurals FINAL
    All 17 plural resources (12 from Batch 10, 5 from Batch 02)

    Reviewed by: Elena Morales (es-batch-10-review.md, 2026-03-21)

    Fixes applied from review:
      H-06  notifications_unread zero form changed from "Sin notificaciones por leer"
            to "Sin notificaciones no leídas" to match the "sin leer" pattern used
            in the one/other forms and to correctly translate "unread" (state) rather
            than "to be read" (pending action)

    Validation notes:
      - All 12 Batch 10 plural resources match English source quantity forms (zero/one/other)
      - Gender agreement verified correct across all noun-adjective pairs
      - Format specifiers (%d) present in all other forms, absent from one forms where
        the literal "1" is hardcoded (Batch 10 pattern)
